text: America's Next Top Model, Cycle 14 is the fourteenth season of America's Next Top Model. This cycle includes 13 contestants. The winner was 24-year-old Krista White from Pine Bluff, Arkansas. ==Contestants== (In alphabetical order) * Brenda Arens * Alasia Ballard * Raina Hein * Tatianna Kern * Gabrielle Kniery * Simone Lewis * Anslee Payne-Franklin * Angelea Preston * Naduah Rugely * Jessica Serfaty * Alexandra Underwood * Ren Vokes * Krista White ==Episodes== 1\. casting episode 2\. *Best: Jessica Serfaty *Worst: Alasia Ballard & Gabrielle Kniery *Eliminated: Gabrielle Kniery 3\. *Best: Raina Hein *Worst: Naduah Rugely & Ren Vokes *Eliminated: Naduah Rugely 4\. *Best: Alasia Ballard *Worst: Brenda Arens & Ren Vokes *Eliminated: Ren Vokes 5\. *Best: Alasia Ballard *Worst: Anslee Payne-Franklin & Simone Lewis *Eliminated: Simone Lewis 6\. *Best: Jessica Serfaty *Worst: Tatianna Kern & Alexandra Underwood *Eliminated: Tatianna Kern 7\. *Best: Angelea Preston *Worst: Alasia Ballard & Brenda Arens *Eliminated: Brenda Arens 8\. *Best: Krista White *Worst: Alexandra Underwood & Anslee Payne-Franklin *Eliminated: Anslee Payne-Franklin 9\. *Best: Krista White *Worst: Alasia Ballard & Jessica Serfaty *Eliminated: Alasia Ballard 10\. *Best: Krista White *Worst: Jessica Serfaty & Raina Hein *Eliminated: Jessica Serfaty 11\. *Best: Krista White *Worst: Alexandra Underwood, Raina Hein & Angelea Preston *Eliminated: Alexandra Underwood & Angelea Preston *Final Two: Raina Hein & Krista White *Winner: Krista White ==Notes== Category:America's Next Top Model
